Unseen_LLAMA_ZS_Hadoop_1:
After Scheduling: PendingReds:<*> ScheduledMaps:<*> ScheduledReds:<*> AssignedMaps:<*> AssignedReds:<*> CompletedMaps:<*> CompletedReds:<*> ContAlloc:<*> ContRel:<*> HostLocal:<*> RackLocal:<*>


### Solution:
```python
def extract_template(log_message):
    template = ""
    for char in log_message:
        if char.isalpha():
            template += char
        else:
            template += "<*>"
    return template
```
